sentences: Lobi Traoré (1961 – 1 June 2010) was a Malian musician.
His breakthrough album, Bamako, produced by Ali Farka Touré, was released in 1994.
It was voted one of the best rock albums of the year by Libération and one of the best world music albums by Le Monde.
